Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:04.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,このあたりイチバン見晴らしの良いあの木に登って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:12.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,あの子が笑う 無邪気に笑う 夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:36.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,空を泳いだ魚の向こうじっと目を凝らせば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:43.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,町の隅っこ色褪せてゆく日々がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:47.83,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆびきりしたままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:50.80,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,サヨナラしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:59.80,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,果たされる日を待ってこの木に宿るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:03.91,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,何回も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:08.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのたび涙する
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:11.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まって動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:16.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのすべてを確かめるように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:24.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら やまびこが聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:04.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}爬上这一带视野最美的那棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:12.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}孩子笑了 笑得天真无邪 她看到了梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:36.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}定定地盯着空中畅游的鱼儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:43.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}小镇每个角落里渐渐褪色的日子浮现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:47.83,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}拉钩上吊百年不变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:50.80,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}即使分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:59.80,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}等待约定实现的心情也寄托在这颗树上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:03.91,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}一遍一遍地重复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:08.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}每次都止不住泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:11.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}停下来又继续走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:16.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}仿佛是要印证这一切似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:24.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}山间回音响不绝 你说是不是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========ED================
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:43.08,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,虫にくわれた草の実の先で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:48.16,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,跳ねるバッタを 捕まえたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:52.84,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,木漏れ日が射す 岩場の上で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:57.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,駄菓子屋で買った シャボン玉吹いて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:20:01.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,春夏秋冬が踊る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:07.86,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽と月が時計の針
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:15.57,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,のびのびと巡る 七色の空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:25.39,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,ここは世界一優しいおかえりが待ってる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:34.26,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,埃かぶった思い出が 何より宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:44.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも変わらない愛しさが 出迎えてくれる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:56.75,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら また季節が歌ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:22.24,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,のんびりと歌うから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:27.04,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,のんきな風が吹いた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:36.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,すすきの穂が寂しそうに揺れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:42.57,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,遠くで聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:45.76,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,「帰っておいで」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:59.38,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,ここは世界一優しい おかえりが待ってる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:04.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,さりげない日常 ふわりと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:08.34,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,抱きしめてくれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:18.44,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,ここは世界一暖かい 春が訪れる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.66,0:22:27.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,みんなみんな大好きな人 大好きなふるさと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:27.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,りぴーと！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:37.29,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも変わらない愛しさが 出迎えてくれる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.42,0:22:49.08,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら また季節が歌ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:43.08,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,遁着虫儿吃过的草籽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:48.16,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我们抓到了蹦跳的蚱蜢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:52.84,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,阳光从树叶缝隙照到石头上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:57.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我们坐在上面吹着在零食店买的肥皂泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:20:01.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,春夏秋冬在舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:07.86,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳和月亮是时钟的指针
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:15.57,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢悠悠地在七色天空中转圈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:25.39,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是全世界最美好的地方 是有人等待我们回家的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:34.26,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,那些封尘的记忆 就是最珍贵的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:44.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一个可爱的地方 总是热情欢迎我们的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:56.75,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,竖起耳朵来 又能听到季节的歌声哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:22.24,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}我们悠闲地歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:27.04,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}享受悠扬的清风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.14,0:21:36.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}狗尾草的穂尖寂寞地摇摆着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:42.57,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}远远地就能听得到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:45.76,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}「快回来哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:59.38,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里是全世界最美好的地方 是有人等待我们回家的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:04.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}那些平平淡淡的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:08.34,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}轻轻地拥抱我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:18.44,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里是全世界最温暖的地方 是春天到访的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.66,0:22:27.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里有我们最喜欢的人 是我们最喜欢的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:27.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}REPEAT！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:37.29,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}这是一个可爱的地方 总是热情欢迎我们的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.42,0:22:49.08,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}竖起耳朵来 又能听到季节的歌声哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========Story================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修路工程完成之后路变得焕然一新呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完午饭大家一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩一会就过去卖零食的那里也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想玩妖精游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小鞠也扮妖精吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不扮妖精扮人类就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我和小夏扮妖精吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说我也玩不了妖精游戏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样把手伸向前面 身体前倾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边大叫「哇哇」一边往前跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏兴奋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啦 樱花开花的时候我们去赏花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:29.49,title,NTP,0,0,0,,一\N年\N过\N去\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扫除也完了 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔子先生 我们还会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 小夏让我们帮她把忘在课桌里面的尺子拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把钥匙放回去之后去教室一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:02:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那根树枝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是传说中的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来只是根树枝呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我在小学入学的时候带来学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经一年了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 找到尺子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑滑的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海前辈又上蜡了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 一会有空去玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦 要玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去附近的竹林 大家一起去采竹笋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照顾兔子的工作都做完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 一会可以去我们家山上采竹笋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和萤约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹笋… 原来已经到这个季节了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那姐姐也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没有采过竹笋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,采竹笋呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得最近我有点花粉症呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她今天才乘夜行巴士回来 到家还没多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让她休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把其他人也叫过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}对呢 大家都喜欢竹笋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也没有那么累…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啦 采到竹笋之后用来做刺身吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃刺身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外去采竹笋得带铲子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们兴致好高呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}铲子是放在外面的仓库吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺身是好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}还要带锄头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你们有听我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}也叫上卖零食的她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呢 一会我打电话给她们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我没说不去呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 其实我没说不去呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐也去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱她们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家已经到了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 我们迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:05:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱是第一次见呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子是我们家养的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它想去散步 所以就带它一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日高君 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日高君——
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 这孩子叫佩奇…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到竹笋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把竹笋周围的土挖开之后就叫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用锄头切出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹笋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挖竹笋的时候要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜姬可能会住在竹笋里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辉 辉夜姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我也听说过这事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹笋里面会住着人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为那肯定是谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把竹笋房子弄坏的话他们就很可怜了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就没办法采竹笋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是开个玩笑 没想到她真信了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚说完没办法告诉她那是骗人的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是这么说 不过应该不是全部都住着人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要是有住人的话 你不觉得他会很可怜吗 小小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然这么觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 只要确认过里面有没有人住就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那样办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们开始采竹笋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根竹笋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 小小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小鞠也来确认下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 你那边有竹笋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 影姐 我们来比一下谁采得多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会输给影姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 想赢我你还得修炼几年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇挖土好快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐 我们可不能输给佩奇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}佩奇……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂…佩奇在吃竹笋呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐 我们也不能输哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真想吃吗 还是输给它算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挖成这样就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让姐姐拿锄头过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗姐是在这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个人在干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,采到根大的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来做刺身的话 尖端是黄色的最好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃起来没那么涩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那吃我这根竹笋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 看起来不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来我家吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又甜又软 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是春天的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芥末放太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像用鼻子用力喷气就会舒服点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 这个杂煮真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加了一点辣味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我想去秘密基地 很久没去过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好哦 一直没去过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就放在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要封印起来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午睡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打地铺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要去晒太阳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暖暖的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在光合作用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呀 『晒太阳』里面的ぼっこ是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,400,0,,{\fs32}日向ぼっこ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢 是『暖和』的变体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:11.08,*Default,NTP,80,0,0,,{\fs32}ほっこり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年开得比往年要早呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啦 我和萤约好了等樱花开了就一起去赏花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做便当带去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用啦 我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕你受伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有前辈给我做的话 我会很不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那来我家一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就那么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们明天去赏花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再等一会竹笋饭就做好了 妈妈会给我们盛起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是樱饼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还没有包上叶子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华你们可以帮下忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边有脱过盐的腌樱花叶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用它包起来就可以了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉只有樱花叶很无聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试用海苔之类的来卷一下怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我们不是做饭团呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那昆布呢 昆布卷感觉不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那太甜了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那芝士怎么样 那个很时髦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:12:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锅那边还没有调味 还得等一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是流动告示 还有我们村采的蕨菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 谢谢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在聊天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还要谈很久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去那边等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天气也很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是晒太阳的好日子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得这么暖和 光坐在这有点无聊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同意莲酱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过阿姨让我们不要去玩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是这么说啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那来说点有趣的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海先说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我说一下昨天做的梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦里面出现了巨大的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物大得只能看到它的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,膝盖上方都已经穿过大气层了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用导弹没办法打倒它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是全世界人民就以眼还眼 以足还足
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起踢它膝盖把它打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们觉得有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我没在听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈她们聊得停不下来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当做不好就没法去赏花了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们来玩打手背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在之前的学校也玩过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在最下面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手慢了 不要拍太大力呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 假动作啦假动作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次就骗不到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拍太大力了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就轮到姐姐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 怎么大家都逃了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这游戏就是这么玩的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不玩了不玩了 我去倒杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也帮我倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的事情自己去做呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给自己倒和给大家倒都一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 萤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们做什么呢 小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再玩一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人就不好玩了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝴蝶 有蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我 蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啦来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那边啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没捕虫网很难抓呀 蝴蝶去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞到我够不到的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 蝴蝶跑掉了 我想去看看光鱼主公
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲤鱼吗 要去看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们俩不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 使人干活之后就自顾自地跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们俩去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫一下试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:17:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海 莲华 饮料拿过来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶我一会再喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果汁 果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于聊完了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去赏花啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.52,0:17:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 聊完天了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聊完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思让你们等了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈做好杂煮了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微等等 我马上盛起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人一会就会追上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是荠菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摇一下就会有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢莲酱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴士来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就可以了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们吃樱饼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得先吃便当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那种规定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜的东西要做饭后甜品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在了在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了三明治哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有海苔卷 炒面和鸡蛋卷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给你们带零食了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下多了好多吃的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Party Party
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那开吃之前大家一起拍张照片怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 笑一个
